{"tid":1572794,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"為健康，人人都需要按摩鎚","createTime":"2019-09-15T18:35:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-16T09:10:21.000Z","uid":61161,"like":22,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"76a5b2ce6cd510611646c29193fdc95491f4c562","tid":1572794,"uid":61161,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T18:35:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ysnoZZL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FysnoZZL.jpg&h=238e3fb4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n話說有一次，媽咪買咗枝按摩鎚返屋企，主要拎黎打一啲肌肉酸痛/肩嘅位置<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n然後，我媽咪貪得意拎黎打咗我膊頭幾下，有一下打咗落舊骨到，痛到我覺得骨裂咗咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過，小心使用應該就無咩野問題嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n做完運動用都幾好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 如果買把按摩槍去到成千銀都真係幾貴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 呢啲唔知邊度有得買，但價錢應該Around $50有一件<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但千奇唔好拎黎扑人，但估應該痛到仆街，好似比鎚仔打中咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n希望幫到對得電腦/手機多嘅巴絲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a53c491da646897452a45eeabc4e8a811176642","tid":1572794,"uid":61161,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T18:38:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SWZR8VL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSWZR8VL.jpg&h=88ed90ad&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n張圖好似出唔到"},{"pid":"9d46d08e78c03d8f58118ac4236280556ab7f03a","tid":1572794,"uid":61161,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T18:39:51.000Z","msg":"有無幫推？"},{"pid":"af9a159664f6ee96dac681468c83f5caff215790","tid":1572794,"uid":137371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T18:40:03.000Z","msg":"齊來做骨妹<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/tongue.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d2b06ec884ac5ff13ba007890187957814e98e2e","tid":1572794,"uid":137371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T18:40:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/smile.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"45a0e340ef932a241638895bbfc6b43ab6e7d1d2","tid":1572794,"uid":61161,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T18:42:19.000Z","msg":"唔信嘅話，大家可以試下用呢舊野按摩下，幾work<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 試下打自己，左唔好打骨/打頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d15133a3f25df127c126351e32366aa7024597fb","tid":1572794,"uid":60260,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T18:43:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1637d9b153fc730e2132cb475e3af6b6a20edcce","tid":1572794,"uid":61161,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T18:43:31.000Z","msg":"有無人有類似經驗？<br />\n<br />\n真心痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea4f6410329430fda11d1397b0363c6ab66aa812","tid":1572794,"uid":321231,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T18:46:20.000Z","msg":"最好一人一枝，幾十枝一齊按<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />一定好舒服"},{"pid":"20ae87470f1803f2ca8519f0bb3778395b0be61a","tid":1572794,"uid":315145,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T18:47:09.000Z","msg":"平時打開波肌肉酸痛 係時候要買支用下"},{"pid":"a1522aa9f98c008d26ff1a995b1ae806fbfa5ef7","tid":1572794,"uid":3206,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T18:56:22.000Z","msg":"條彈弓好易fing到自己<br />\n小心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"68d021f516bbc14150ed158acdf7894ed1661101","tid":1572794,"uid":61161,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a1522aa9f98c008d26ff1a995b1ae806fbfa5ef7","tid":1572794,"uid":3206,"like":0,"dislike":